@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rzoems(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.06 * tmp + 0.51)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.94) * 0.08) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.96) * (v1 + 0.42 - v1 + 0.93)))
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp((v2 + 0.03 - tmp + 0.31)))
    data[tid] = v0
